{"id":150998,"link":"https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/2011/05/欧盟内政问题专员就难民问题发表讲话/","date":"2011-05-09T09:00:25Z","modified":"2011-05-09T09:00:25Z","title":"欧盟内政问题专员就难民问题发表讲话","content":"<div>\n<p><span lang=\"ZH-CN\">布鲁塞尔</span></p>\n<p><span lang=\"ZH-CN\">欧盟内政问题专员玛尔姆斯特伦</span><span>(Cecilia Malmström)</span><span lang=\"ZH-CN\">针对最近以来的北非难民潮呼吁欧洲各国团结一致。她说，欧盟必须帮助那些受难民潮严重影响的成员国以及北非国家。我们不应当忘记正是突尼斯和埃及安置了过去几周逃离利比亚的大约</span><span>65</span><span lang=\"ZH-CN\">万难民中的大多数人。这位专员还宣布，周四在欧盟国家内政部长会议上将审核各成员国接纳非洲难民的承诺。</span></p>\n</div>\n<p><img src=\"http://api.mixpanel.com/track/?data=eyJldmVudCI6ICJmdWxsdGV4dGltcHJlc3Npb24iLCAicHJvcGVydGllcyI6IHsidG9rZW4iOiAiYTRhNDYwYTM5MDRlZWU4ZmY1ZTAyNGVhNGJkZTdhYzIifX0=&#038;ip=1&#038;img=1\" width=\"1\" height=\"1\" border=\"0\" /><img src=\"http://pixel.quantserve.com/pixel/p-89EKCgBk8MZdE.gif\" border=\"0\" height=\"1\" width=\"1\" /><a href=\"http://api.mixpanel.com/track/?data=eyJldmVudCI6ICJmdWxsdGV4dGNsaWNrIiwgInByb3BlcnRpZXMiOiB7InRva2VuIjogImE0YTQ2MGEzOTA0ZWVlOGZmNWUwMjRlYTRiZGU3YWMyIn19&#038;ip=1&#038;redirect=http://talkita.com/wrap?url=http%3A%2F%2Fwww.dw-world.de%2Fdw%2Farticle%2F0%2C%2C15060578%2C00.html%3Fmaca%3Dchi-rss-chi-all-1127-rdf&#038;title=%E6%AC%A7%E7%9B%9F%E5%86%85%E6%94%BF%E9%97%AE%E9%A2%98%E4%B8%93%E5%91%98%E5%B0%B1%E9%9A%BE%E6%B0%91%E9%97%AE%E9%A2%98%E5%8F%91%E8%A1%A8%E8%AE%B2%E8%AF%9D\">Chat about this story w/ Talkita</a></p>\n<form method=\"POST\" action=\"http://www.feedblitz.com/f/f.fbz?AddNewUserDirect\">\n定期获得翻墙信息？<a href=\"http://www.feedblitz.com/f/?Sub=750556\">请电邮订阅数字时代</a> <br /><input name=\"EMAIL\" maxlength=\"64\" type=\"text\" size=\"25\" value=\"\"><br />\n<input name=\"FEEDID\" type=\"hidden\" value=\"750556\"><br />\n<input name=\"PUBLISHER\" type=\"hidden\" value=\"7485568\"><br />\n<input type=\"submit\" value=\"订阅!\"><br />\n</form>\n","author":176,"categories":[8779],"tags":[]}